{"tid":6771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朱 經 緯 警 棍 毆 打 途 人 兩 周 年","createTime":"2016-11-27T13:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T03:36:22.000Z","uid":609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8fe3665600f7d91e6a37ca96c15051fb6a150000","tid":6771,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:59:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.giphy.com/3o6ZsTQgaohtYfFFHa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.giphy.com%2F3o6ZsTQgaohtYfFFHa.gif&h=e20e5b0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161125/large/1480069723_18c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161125%2Flarge%2F1480069723_18c6.jpg&h=872900fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n退休警司朱經緯涉警棍毆打途人至今兩周年，早前警方完成刑事調查，惟律政司仍未決定是否就案件提出刑事檢控。民權觀察成員王浩賢批評，案件兩年仍懸而未決，屬不合理拖延，認為律政司需向公眾交代，盡快處理案件。有市民就自發周六晚在發起遊行，要求警方盡快拘捕朱經緯。<br />\n<br />\n旺角鳩嗚團發起周六晚遊行，晚上10時半從旺角行人專用區百老匯戲院對面出發，遊行至旺角警署遞交請願信，要求警方盡快拘捕朱經緯。發起人之一細儀表示，已向警方申請不反對通知書。<br />\n王浩賢表示，案件並不複雜，警方早前亦已完成調查，看不到有任何原因需拖延至今，「係唔合理拖延，應該盡快處理，而且公眾好關注案件，所以律政司是否檢控，都應該公開有關理據向大眾交代。」他又指，聯合國禁止酷刑委員會於去年已要求警方公開《警察通例》及其他相關的武力使用指引，惟至今警方仍未有任何回應，認為警方有責任向公眾交代使用武力的指引。<br />\n律政司發言人回覆指，就相關案件，投訴警察課已向律政司提交調查報告及資料，尋求進一步法律意見。部門會小心和全面考慮適用法律、相關證據和《檢控守則》，向警方提供意見，並就是否提出檢控作出決定，惟現階段不適宜作具體評論。<br />\n警方稱，投訴警察課已完成相關個案的刑事調查，並將個案交予律政司以徵詢進一步法律意見，現階段不作進一步評論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">朱蛇</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25fe2f696d62d1fe0b6806b1826abe030c9d7afb","tid":6771,"uid":84,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:00:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92841c05406912345449c8dd910e1642807f6075","tid":6771,"uid":21509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:01:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bddfa64df75b3afce55cef82734fdc0315fd3bf","tid":6771,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:02:07.000Z","msg":"沙田棍妖"},{"pid":"350f452fdc03066ad9b743ad3730208150653563","tid":6771,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:02:13.000Z","msg":"一齊加入force呢個大家庭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n維持治安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打撚死班搞屎棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n長糧已袋 樓已買 民已移 理撚得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f787a8bf902d669ae9973c8d1f1ac795993731d","tid":6771,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:02:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Hong Kong Police Force</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0299dd206a1ce5ea574028f969c9ad55c7b44690","tid":6771,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:03:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">岩喇！大大力扑班港獨狗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d704a45f458d4a87959ec3b272ba80fd3d21d896","tid":6771,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0